# Copy to .env.local (recommended) or use .env — use ONE Clerk application for the whole repo.
# Keys must match backend/.env (same "Instances" page in Clerk Dashboard).
#
# If you see: "jwk-kid-mismatch" or "Handshake token verification failed":
# - You switched Clerk apps, or frontend/backend keys disagree, or old keyless cookies remain.
# - Fix: align keys below with backend, then clear site data for localhost (cookies: __session, __client_uat, etc.).
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...

NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
